right now.\\\"\", \"from\": 2136, \"to\": 2209, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"another silver\", \"from\": 2153, \"to\": 2167}, {\"ngram\": \"our thoughts\", \"from\": 2185, \"to\": 2197}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hewett is looking to secure a golden slam in singles too, scarred by defeats to Reid in Rio and Tokyo.\", \"from\": 2211, \"to\": 2313, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2299, \"end\": 2302, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"score\": 0.978208505773662, \"rank\": 0.022276942080851098, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\"}, {\"begin\": 2307, \"end\": 2312, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.991489101228912, \"rank\": 0.008583955933564282, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Hewett\", \"from\": 2211, \"to\": 2217}, {\"ngram\": \"a golden slam\", \"from\": 2239, \"to\": 2252}, {\"ngram\": \"singles\", \"from\": 2256, \"to\": 2263}, {\"ngram\": \"defeats\", \"from\": 2280, \"to\": 2287}, {\"ngram\": \"Reid\", \"from\": 2291, \"to\": 2295}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His historic win at Wimbledon just a few weeks ago means he could complete the set here, where he last won the French Open singles in 2021.\", \"from\": 2315, \"to\": 2454, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His historic win\", \"from\": 2315, \"to\": 2331}, {\"ngram\": \"Wimbledon\", \"from\": 2335, \"to\": 2344}, {\"ngram\": \"the set\", \"from\": 2390, \"to\": 2397}, {\"ngram\": \"the French Open singles\", \"from\": 2422, \"to\": 2445}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Seeded No 1, he brushed aside Dutch rival Ruben Spaargarten in his quarter-final, although Reid was beaten by Argentina's Gustavo Fern\\u00e1ndez, who could well be Hewett's greatest threat.\", \"from\": 2456, \"to\": 2640, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2486, \"end\": 2491, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.8042448201788585, \"rank\": 0.15626744164143772, \"text\": \"Dutch\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}, {\"begin\": 2566, \"end\": 2575, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9803328636740698, \"rank\": 0.012004135691107637, \"text\": \"Argentina\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2578, \"end\": 2595, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gustavo_Fern\\u00e1ndez_(tennis)\", \"score\": 0.9999999548863353, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gustavo Fern\\u00e1ndez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gustavo_Fern\\u00e1ndez_(tennis)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gustavo_Fern\\u00e1ndez_(tennis)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Reid\", \"from\": 2547, \"to\": 2551}, {\"ngram\": \"Hewett's greatest threat\", \"from\": 2615, \"to\": 2639}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not feel the pressure of our record, we take confidence from it,\\\" said Reid.\", \"from\": 2642, \"to\": 2724, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the pressure\", \"from\": 2657, \"to\": 2669}, {\"ngram\": \"our record\", \"from\": 2673, \"to\": 2683}, {\"ngram\": \"confidence\", \"from\": 2693, \"to\": 2703}, {\"ngram\": \"Reid\", \"from\": 2719, \"to\": 2723}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are used to these courts, used to these conditions and we have had great results here.\", \"from\": 2725, \"to\": 2815, \"entities\": [], \"nou