404, \"to\": 3430}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am not retiring from the sport as a whole.\", \"from\": 3447, \"to\": 3492, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 3471, \"to\": 3480}, {\"ngram\": \"a whole\", \"from\": 3484, \"to\": 3491}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am carrying on till my body tells me to stop but I am ready to start a life away from the court,\\\" said Lapthorne, after a 6-1 6-1 defeat to top seeds Niels Vink and Sam Schroder.\", \"from\": 3493, \"to\": 3673, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3645, \"end\": 3655, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Niels_Vink\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Niels Vink\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Niels_Vink\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Niels_Vink\"}, {\"begin\": 3660, \"end\": 3663, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Winchester\", \"score\": 0.9985179227884806, \"rank\": 0.00142475753288976, \"text\": \"Sam\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Winchester\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Winchester\"}, {\"begin\": 3664, \"end\": 3672, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Schroders\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4596909937104268e-18, \"text\": \"Schroder\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Schroders\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Schroders\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my body\", \"from\": 3515, \"to\": 3522}, {\"ngram\": \"a life\", \"from\": 3564, \"to\": 3570}, {\"ngram\": \"the court\", \"from\": 3581, \"to\": 3590}, {\"ngram\": \"Lapthorne\", \"from\": 3598, \"to\": 3607}, {\"ngram\": \"a 6-1 6-1 defeat\", \"from\": 3615, \"to\": 3631}, {\"ngram\": \"top seeds\", \"from\": 3635, \"to\": 3644}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That was my last Paralympic match.\", \"from\": 3675, \"to\": 3710, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my last Paralympic match\", \"from\": 3685, \"to\": 3709}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's been such a journey and it feels bittersweet.\", \"from\": 3711, \"to\": 3761, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"such a journey\", \"from\": 3721, \"to\": 3735}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The vibes and crowds here have been so special, I feel ready to leave it.\", \"from\": 3762, \"to\": 3835, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The vibes\", \"from\": 3762, \"to\": 3771}, {\"ngram\": \"crowds\", \"from\": 3776, \"to\": 3782}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You think you can do this forever but when you wake up and realise that's not the case, it's weird.\", \"from\": 3836, \"to\": 3935, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the case\", \"from\": 3914, \"to\": 3922}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's been an emotional 24 hours, it's not easy to win four Paralympic medals in wheelchair tennis.\", \"from\": 3937, \"to\": 4036, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an emotional 24 hours\", \"from\": 3948, \"to\": 3969}, {\"ngram\": \"four Paralympic medals\", \"from\": 3992, \"to\": 4014}, {\"ngram\": \"wheelchair tennis\", \"from\": 4018, \"to\": 4035}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's time for me to leave this career behind and I am leaving on a centre court at a grand slam venue, in front of a huge crowd.\", \"from\": 4038, \"to\": 4167, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 4044, \"to\": 4048}, {\"ngram\": \"this career\", \"from\": 4065, \"to\": 4076}, {\"ngram\": \"a centre court\", \"from\": 4104, \"to\": 4118}, {\"ngram\": \"a grand slam venue\", \"from\": 4122, \"to\": 4140}, {\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 4145, \"to\": 4150}, {\"ngram\": \"a huge crowd\", \"from\": 4154, \"to\": 4166}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Other things need to take priority over playing tennis matches and that's not happened since I was 16 years old.\", \"from\": 4169, \"to\": 4282, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Other things\", \"from\": 4170, \"to\": 4182}, {\"ngram\": \"priority\", \"from\": 4196, \"to\": 4204}, {\"ngram\": \"tennis matches\", \"from\": 4218, \"to\": 4232}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I said I would not wear this shirt unless I could win a gold medal and I do not think I can do that in Los Angeles.\\\"\", \"from\": 4284, \"to\": 4401, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4388, \"end\": 4399, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999919082256, \"rank\": 8.090281502172926e-09, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this shirt\", \"from\": 4309, \"to\": 4319}, {\"ngram\": \"a gold medal\", \"from\": 4339, \"to\": 4351}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Slade admitted the pressure of the build-up to these Games was tough, his selection only confirmed a few weeks ago.\", \"from\": 4403, \"to\": 4518, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4403, \"end\": 4408, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Slade\", \"score\": 0.9999999986116563, \"rank\": 1.3883752500174862e-09, \"text\": \"Slade\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q215380\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Slade\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Slade\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the pressure\", \"from\": 4418, \"to\": 4430}, {\"ngram\": \"the build-up\", \"from\": 4434, \"to\": 4446}, {\"ngram\": \"these Games\", \"from\": 4450, \"to\": 4461}, {\"ngram\": \"his selection\", \"from\": 4473, \"to\": 4486}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But he has underlined his status as a rising star of the sport with some big performances at clutch moments, especially during the semi-final win over Brazil's Leandro Pena and Ymanitu Silva.\", \"from\": 4520, \"to\": 4711, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4671, \"end\": 4677, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999997162